'''β2微球蛋白'''（{{lang-en|β<sub>2</sub>-microglobulin}}，缩写'''B2M'''）是[[MHC_Ⅰ类分子|MHC1類分子]]分子的组成部分之一，在所有有核的细胞中（即不包括[[红细胞|红细胞]]）都有表达<ref name="entrez_567">{{Cite web|title=B2M beta-2-microglobulin [Homo sapiens (human)]|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=gene&Cmd=ShowDetailView&TermToSearch=567|access-date=2022-03-16|work=NCBI|language=en}}</ref><ref name="pmid3312414">{{Cite journal|title=The human beta 2-microglobulin gene. Primary structure and definition of the transcriptional unit|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/3312414|last=Güssow|first=D.|last2=Rein|first2=R.|date=1987-11-01|journal=Journal of Immunology (Baltimore, Md.: 1950)|issue=9|volume=139|pages=3132–3138|issn=0022-1767|pmid=3312414|last3=Ginjaar|first3=I.|last4=Hochstenbach|first4=F.|last5=Seemann|first5=G.|last6=Kottman|first6=A.|last7=Ploegh|first7=H. L.|access-date=2022-03-16|archive-date=2022-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105155839/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/3312414/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在人类基因组中，β2微球蛋白<ref name="pmid4586824">{{Cite journal|title=Complete amino acid sequence of β 2 -microglobulin|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/bi00748a001|last=Cunningham|first=Bruce A.|last2=Wang|first2=John L.|date=1973-11|journal=Biochemistry|issue=24|doi=10.1021/bi00748a001|volume=12|pages=4811–4822|language=en|issn=0006-2960|pmid=4586824|last3=Berggard|first3=Ingemar|last4=Peterson|first4=Per A.|access-date=2022-03-16|archive-date=2022-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220316192518/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/bi00748a001|dead-url=no}}</ref>由''B2M'' [[基因|基因]]所编码<ref name="pmid3312414"/><ref name="pmid6171820">{{Cite journal|title=Use of synthetic oligonucleotides as hybridization probes: isolation of cloned cDNA sequences for human beta 2-microglobulin.|url=https://pnas.org/doi/full/10.1073/pnas.78.11.6613|last=Suggs|first=S V|last2=Wallace|first2=R B|date=1981-11|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=11|doi=10.1073/pnas.